ault value is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionWrapsCoordinates"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel":{"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing an integer; specifies the minimum zoom level at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"which to create vector tiles. The default value is 0.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionminimumzoomlevel","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionMinimumZoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.sw